OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FFuel protesters in Dublin city centre
OL,8,Fwere "ambushed" by an "army" of public
OL,9,Forder police, according to a spokesman
OL,10,Ffor the blockaders.
OL,12,FThe blockade of the capital's main
OL,13,Fthoroughfare O'Connell Street was
OL,14,Fcleared in a late-night police
OL,15,Foperation, ahead of an emergency
OL,16,FCabinet meeting on Sunday to sign off
OL,17,Fon measures the Irish Government hopes
OL,18,Fwill bring all protests over fuel
OL,19,Fcosts to an end.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@OO]pD@WOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Irish police service An Garda
OL,8,FSiochana conducted a separate
OL,9,Foperation to clear another blockade at
OL,10,FGalway docks, where gardai with
OL,11,Fshields and protective gear clashed
OL,12,Fwith protesters at the harbour.
OL,14,FThe protests ` including blockades of
OL,15,FIreland's only oil refinery in Cork
OL,16,Fand another depot in Limerick `
OL,17,Fstrangled fuel distribution across the
OL,18,Fcountry and prompted an escalated
OL,19,Fpolicing response that resulted in
OL,20,Fseveral arrests and public order units
OL,21,Fdeployed three times.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FParticipants ` largely led by
OL,8,Fhauliers, farmers, and agricultural
OL,9,Fworkers ` began distinct but co-
OL,10,Fordinated action on Tuesday with slow-
OL,11,Fmoving convoys and outright stoppages
OL,12,Fon major motorways, as well as
OL,13,Fblockades of critical infrastructure
OL,14,Fwhich had largely wound down by midday
OL,15,Fon Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FOver six consecutive days, spokesmen
OL,8,Fhad called on the Government to take
OL,9,Furgent action to reduce fuel costs
OL,10,Fwhich they say are at unsustainable
OL,11,Flevels and will lead to people going
OL,12,Fout of business.
OL,14,FElsewhere, protesters voted to leave a
OL,15,Fblockade at a depot in Foynes, Co
OL,16,FLimerick while several trucks were
OL,17,Fgranted access to Rosslare Europort.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSpeaking about the overnight Garda
OL,8,Foperation on O'Connell Street, Dublin
OL,9,Fprotest spokesman Christopher Duffy
OL,10,Fsaid: "We got absolutely ambushed here
OL,11,Flast night by what I can only describe
OL,12,Fas an army of (public order gardai)."
OL,14,FHe said protesters were "pulling out
OL,15,Fof O'Connell Street" because gardai
OL,16,Fhad threatened to tow their vehicles,
OL,17,Fwhich he said could damage them.
OL,19,F"So we have no choice, financially we
OL,20,Fhave to move the vehicles."
OL,26,@rD@GOUtD@eO]vD@YOUwD@TO]{D@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe called for rural TDs and
OL,8,Findependents "propping up the
OL,9,FGovernment" to call a motion of no
OL,10,Fconfidence in the coalition.
OL,12,FAsked if the overall protests are now
OL,13,Fover, he said: "I don't think so."
OL,15,FMeanwhile, the Defence Forces assisted
OL,16,Fgardai with clearing a makeshift
OL,17,Fbarrier erected by protesters
OL,18,Fblockading Galway docks.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@KO]uD@POUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FFootage posted on social media by An
OL,8,FGarda Siochana showed a Defence Forces
OL,9,Fheavy-lift recovery truck ` nicknamed
OL,10,F'the Beast' ` driving through the
OL,11,Fbarrier constructed with pallets and
OL,12,Flogs, while a garda helicopter
OL,13,Fmonitored overhead.
OL,15,FA second heavy-lift recovery truck
OL,16,Foperated by the Defence Forces was
OL,17,Falso at the scene while gardai worked
OL,18,Fto restore access to the harbour, as
OL,19,Fthe Public Order Unit members with
OL,20,Fplastic shields pushed against a line
OL,21,Fof demonstrators.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe coalition Government is expected
OL,8,Fto sign off on fuel-cost measures on
OL,9,FSunday evening, but it remains to be
OL,10,Fseen if it will convince protesters to
OL,11,Fcall off any return to action when the
OL,12,Freturn of schools on Monday adds to
OL,13,Fpressure on the roads.
OL,15,FOn Saturday, gardai first cleared a
OL,16,Fblockade of the Whitegate oil refinery
OL,17,Fin Co Cork.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIt also saw physical clashes between
OL,8,Fprotesters and gardai, who used pepper
OL,9,Fspray during the hour-long operation
OL,10,Fwhich resecured access for fuel trucks.
OL,12,FGarda Commissioner Justin Kelly had
OL,13,Fvowed to step up enforcement against
OL,14,Ffuel-cost protesters "endangering the
OL,15,Fstate" by blocking critical
OL,16,Finfrastructure.
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FProtesters' demands for meetings with
OL,8,FGovernment were not acceded to but
OL,9,Frelevant ministers held talks with
OL,10,Festablished national representative
OL,11,Fbodies on Friday and Saturday.
OL,13,FThese meetings concluded with a
OL,14,F"substantial" package involving a
OL,15,Ftemporary fuel transport support
OL,16,Fscheme" and "temporary fuel support".
OL,18,FIt is understood the transport support
OL,19,Fscheme will see direct payments to
OL,20,Fbusinesses in the sectors affected by
OL,21,Fhigh fuel costs.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@MO]xD@GO]xD@MOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FA senior source said the scheme will
OL,8,Fbe part of a broader package on the
OL,9,Ffuel crisis.
OL,11,FThe engagements included Irish Road
OL,12,FHaulage Association president Ger
OL,13,FHyland, who said there were "the bones
OL,14,Fof an agreement" with the Government.
OL,16,FHe added he hoped the "substantial
OL,17,Fpackage", understood to include a
OL,18,Fdirect payment scheme, would be agreed
OL,19,Fby Sunday morning.
OL,26,@uD@]OUvD@PO]xD@WOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Cabinet is due to meet at 4pm on
OL,8,FSunday to sign off on the measures.
OL,10,FCommissioner Kelly said the blockades
OL,11,Fof critical infrastructure "resulted
OL,12,Fin fuel shortages that are directly
OL,13,Fimpacting on emergency services such
OL,14,Fas hospitals, the ambulance service
OL,15,Fand the fire service, as well as
OL,16,Fbusinesses and the general public".
OL,18,FHe said: "These are blockades. They
OL,19,Fare not a legitimate form of protest."
OL,26,@sD@\OUxD@bO]zD@JOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FHe added: "We gave the blockaders fair
OL,8,Fwarning that we were moving to
OL,9,Fenforcement and they choose to ignore
OL,10,Fit and continue to hold the country to
OL,11,Fransom."
OL,13,FThe escalated enforcement action came
OL,14,Fas Fuels for Ireland chief executive
OL,15,FKevin McPartlan warned it would "still
OL,16,Ftake 10 days to recover" to normal.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@HO]wD@aOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr McPartlan, who had estimated that
OL,8,Fup to two-thirds of the country's
OL,9,F1,500 filling stations could have ran
OL,10,Fdry by Sunday morning, said the
OL,11,Fsituation is "rapidly changing" due to
OL,12,Fthe garda interventions ` but said
OL,13,Fhundreds of forecourts would still be
OL,14,Fwithout fuel.
OL,16,FWhile fuel truck access to Whitegate
OL,17,Foil refinery was ramping up
OL,18,Fsignificantly, ongoing disruption on
OL,19,Fmajor roads was affecting distribution.
OL,26,@sD@NOUsD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/17
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1776041693
OL,3,CDublin fuel protesters 'ambushed' in
OL,4,Clate-night Garda operation, spokesman
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FBlockades have resulted in full
OL,8,Fclosures of parts of major motorways,
OL,9,Falthough Gardai announced blockades on
OL,10,Fthe M50 at junctions five and seven
OL,11,Fhad been cleared on Sunday morning.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, police in Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fsaid they are "maintaining an ongoing
OL,15,Fassessment" in relation to social
OL,16,Fmedia posts calling for similar
OL,17,Fplanned protests there.
OL,26,@vD@OOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/17
